quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  27,67,Abo abaakaafuwala bagamba nti bwe tulimala okufuuka ettaka ne bakadde baffe ate tulijjibwayo
  27,68,"Mazima ffe ne bakadde baffe okuva edda kino kizze kitulagaanyisibwa (nga tewali kibaawo, n'olwekyo) bino tebiri okugyako nfumo z'abaakulembera"
  27,69,Bagambe (ggwe Muhammad) nti mutambule mu nsi mulabe ngeriki enkomerero ya boonoonyi bwe yali
  27,70,Tonakuwala ku lwabwe era towulira bubi olw'enkwe ze basala
  27,71,Era bagamba nti endagaano eyo erituuka ddi bwe muba nga mwogera mazima
  27,72,"Bagambe nti, si kulwa nga musemberedde ebimu ku ebyo bye musaba okubatuukako mu bwangu"
  27,73,"Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ajjudde ebirungi byagabira abantu, naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebeebaza"
  27,74,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo amanyi ebyo ebifuba bya bwe bye bikweka n'ebyo bye bakola mu lwatu
  27,75,Era tewali kyekusifu kyonna mu ggulu ne munsi wabula nga nakyo Kiri mu kitabo ekiraga buli kimu
  27,76,Mazima Kur’ani eno etegeeza abaana ba Israil ebisinga obungi ebyo bye baawukanamu
  27,77,Era mazima yyo bulungamu na kusaasira eri abakkiriza
  27,78,"Era Mukama omulabiriziwo alitaawulula wakati wa bwe nga abalamula, era yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omumanyi ennyo"
  27,79,"N'olwekyo (ggwe Muhammad) weekwate ku Katonda, mazima ggwe oli ku mazima ameeyolefu"
  27,80,"(Awamu n'ekyo) mazima ggwe tosobola kuwuliza bafu era nga bwotasobola kuwuliza ba kiggala okukoowoola, kasita bakyuka nebakubayo amabega"
  27,81,"Era ggwe tosobola kulungamya ba muzibe noobaggya ku bubuze bwa bwe, tosobola kuwuliza okugyako abo abakkiriza ebigambo byaffe era abo be beewaayo ewa Katonda"
  27,82,"Ekigambo bwe kiribagwaako tugenda kubaggyirayo ensolo okuva mu ttaka eyogere nabo, anti mazima abantu baali tebakakasa bigambo byaffe"